Danny, pare com isso!

193
00:08:37,059 --> 00:08:39,102
Danny, sai de cima dele!

194
00:08:40,229 --> 00:08:41,939
JT:
Ai! Não consigo respirar!

195
00:08:42,022 --> 00:08:43,357
LIBERTY:
Danny, pare!

196
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:44,608
